od construction practices are followed  and that high quality work is completed    Mission Statement  To direct or coordinate the work of architects  engineers  and contractors following construction contract award of all capital outlay projects  construction renovations  and major repairs to insure that all work conforms to plans and specifications  follows good construction practices  and is of good quality  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 